body:
Feels like home

============

Carol Danvers + Fem!Reader

====================

You were an Avenger but before you were one you had a normal life you had a girlfriend who before she was your girlfriend she was your childhood best friend Carol you two would spend hours laughing and joking around

But funny thing was is amazing how quickly things changed between the two of you it was different when she took your hand and the first time she kissed you it felt like magic she was 16 you were 15.

Things just went from there it was like you were ment to be together right from the start since you were friends forever she made you feel things that are only described in fairy tales but when she smiled at you it was like the whole world smiled two.

You were always on Cloud 9 when you were with her she made you feel safe and protected you knew she was the one because your heart knew this was real this was true love she was your home.

When you turned 21 Carol Asked you to marry her of course you said yes to her

You had a beautiful wedding with friends and family but you didn’t care if it was just the two of you because the world melts away when your with her she was like gravity always pulling you towards her always

When carol got her new dream job you couldn’t be more happy for her she would always give her signal to you before a flight.

You would always say to her “fly high baby” she would signal you with “Higher further Faster Baby”

But when she went out on that flight she never came back you got a knock on the door to be told there was an accident and Carol’s plane went down and she died in the crash all they could retrieve was a broken piece of her name tag as they gave there condolences and left you let out a scream your world your universe your home was gone your only reason for living was no longer here your world came crashing down and became dust you had lost the love of your life , your wife , your best friend your Home.

blog.name: fandomtransparents
blog.title: Fandom Transparents
blog.description:
This is my tumblr blog for all my fandom transparents. Send in your requests and I will do my best. If there is a specific photo you want edited please submit them, otherwise just send them in the ask box. I do transparents of characters from TV and Movies only. If you want a larger version of a seen work message me along with which image. 

Tagged list is a list of the main things I post, but feel free to request other things. There is also a page of the actors who are in a lot of the ones I make. 

Please feel free to use but do give me credit. I love seeing what people have done with these. 

My main blog is Fandommember here on tumblr, and if you need anything in a rush please ask me there.
